        "\\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial x} =4x^{3}\\  \\wedge \\  \\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial y} =3y^{2}\\exp \\left( y^{3}+e^{2}\\arctan \\left( z\\right)  \\right)  \\  \\wedge \\  \\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial z} =2\\pi z^{2\\pi -1}\n",
        "\\tag{1.46}\n",
        "$$\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "Por lo tanto, el gradiente de $f$ se calcula como\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.eq-scroll}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\nabla_{\\left( x,y,z\\right)  } f=\\left( \\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial x} ,\\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial y} ,\\frac{\\partial f}{\\partial z} \\right)  =\\left( 4x^{3},3y^{2}\\exp \\left( y^{3}+e^{2}\\arctan \\left( z\\right)  \\right)  ,2\\pi z^{2\\pi -1}\\right)\n",
        "\\tag{1.47}\n",
